WebServicesSection Class

In this Article

Represents the webServices element in the configuration file. This element controls the settings of XML Web services.

Syntax

Declaration

public sealed class WebServicesSection : System.Configuration.ConfigurationSection

Constructors summary

WebServicesSection()

Initializes a new instance of the WebServicesSection class.

Properties summary

ConformanceWarnings

Gets the collection of conformance warnings for the Web Service. This property corresponds to the configurationWarnings element in the configuration file.
Current

Gets a WebServicesSection object that represents the current section.
Diagnostics

Gets or sets the DiagnosticsElement for the WebServicesSection object.
EnabledProtocols

Gets one of the WebServiceProtocols values that indicates the Web service protocol.
Properties
Protocols

Gets the transmission protocol that is used to decrypt data sent from a client browser in an HTTP request.
ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionTypes

Gets the TypeElementCollection that specifies the service description format extension to run within the scope of the configuration file.
SoapEnvelopeProcessing

Gets or sets the SoapEnvelopeProcessingElement for the WebServicesSection object.
SoapExtensionImporterTypes

Gets the TypeElementCollection that specifies the SOAP extensions to run when a service description for an XML Web service within the scope of the configuration file is accessed.
SoapExtensionReflectorTypes

Gets the TypeElementCollection that specifies the SOAP extensions to run when a service description is generated for all XML Web services within the scope of the configuration file.
SoapExtensionTypes

Gets the SoapExtensionTypeElementCollection that specifies the SOAP extensions to run with all XML Web services within the scope of the configuration file.
SoapServerProtocolFactoryType

Gets a TypeElement object that corresponds to the protocol used to call the Web service.
SoapTransportImporterTypes

Gets a TypeElementCollection object that represents the SoapTransportImporterTypes configuration element.
WsdlHelpGenerator

Gets the Web service Help page (an .aspx file) that is displayed to a browser when the browser navigates directly to an ASMX page.
